{"tid":2248934,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"陳雲：人地懵撚到上心口，只是波大，要心口戴罩，香港人面口戴罩呀屌。","createTime":"2020-10-19T03:52:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-19T04:49:11.000Z","uid":228143,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9ea05a500e48af156f948a6b9c82d8805f6db6a6","tid":2248934,"uid":228143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T03:52:32.000Z","msg":"陳雲：鹹濕論政。政治市，國師早起送錢。Covid封城是令民間貧困中產和窮人活動停頓的時間停止（time freeze）大計謀，富豪就頻頻移動，結果當然是富豪賺大錢，半年身家暴漲27%（彭博新聞社）。<br />\n<br />\n玩的是反應時間的差別（球賽叫時間差）。<br />\n各位看過日本AV的時間停止專題嗎？很多溫泉的女人被freeze，鹹濕佬學了時間停頓的咒語，就可以慢慢向各位赤裸美女上下其手。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n世界上，除了瑞典不給國民玩時間停止遊戲，其他國家都玩時間停止，給國際財團去玩弄在溫泉裡面停止活動的赤裸國民。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，懵撚到吖，大陸已經除嗮口罩拼經濟，香港人還在懵戴口罩，行路、食飯都慢撚過人啦。香港被深圳吞併，已經可以預見，因為香港人懵撚到上面口。<br />\n<br />\n人地懵撚到上心口，只是波大，要心口戴罩，香港人面口戴罩呀屌。<br />\n<br />\n呢排食晒藥  講得好岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n買口罩洗手液都買窮人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96ccd1dbf09e99406cc1efc59f673c42649a2e40","tid":2248934,"uid":68860,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T03:58:51.000Z","msg":"Source?"},{"pid":"2b23fbcef3f5c8f77266f76b298601e87acf476d","tid":2248934,"uid":51701,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-19T04:02:37.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><p class=\"center\">扮燒山fans嘅雲糞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O0vOfJ0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO0vOfJ0.jpg&h=d9a57d1e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PGVnkaG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPGVnkaG.jpg&h=22e80bf0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8K3j6QH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8K3j6QH.jpg&h=bc059408&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bsF24Co.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2